name: Chandler Creech
body:
## Welcome to my site

I'm a computer Engineering major at the University of Michigan.

I build cool stuff with both hardware and software, and am experienced with C/C++, assembly, Android dev, and embedded microcontrollers.

## Noteable Projects:
PIC32 C microcontoller based electronic bike kiosk system for University of Michigan Flint campus

Touch screen animation creation device created from an ALtera DE2-115 FPGA development board

Android app allowing users to create animations through drawings and pictures taken. 

Python based MIRC chat bot parser, allowing for many people to simultaneously send keystrokes to my computer through online chat.
